flowchart TD
  PM[PM or Admin] --> Create[Create Project]
  Create --> Project[(projects)]
  Project --> Workspace[Projects workspace]
  Workspace --> Attach[Attach task with task version]
  Attach --> Check{Project active?}
  Check -- no --> Conflict[409 project_archived]
  Check -- yes --> Update[Update task.project_id and version]
  Update --> Mutation[(project_mutations)]
  Update --> Filter[Task workspace project filter]
  Reader[Reader] --> Inspect[Inspect Projects and memberships]
  Reader -. write attempt .-> Forbidden[403 forbidden]
  OtherTenant[Other tenant] -. lookup .-> NotFound[404 project_not_found]
